Boat Battle

- Tutorial page
- Playing board
	- grid based
- Set of boats
- Bigger boats are worth more points
- Scoring system
	- tracking hit rate for score
- computer knows to continue firing near a hit (when it gets a hit)
- qualify input (can't shoot the same spot twice)
- Turn based
- Turn time limit
- randomly generated boat layouts
- different difficulties
- opponent can freeze the other player
- explosions
- sound effects
- power ups
- hint system
- scout plane
